"Something told me 't if I didn't come back and get --" He shuddered;
            then waved his nerveless hand with a vanquished gesture and said, "Tell 'em, Joe, tell
            'em -it ain't any use any more."

Another denial. Tom's uneasiness grew more and more intense under the
            slow torture of these proceedings. The master scanned the ranks of boys -considered a
            while, then turned to the girls:

Tom went to bed that night planning vengeance against Alfred Temple;
            for with shame and repentance Becky had told him all, not forgetting her own treachery;
            but even the longing for vengeance had to give way, soon, to pleasanter musings, and he
            fell asleep at last with Becky's latest words lingering dreamily in his ear --

